{"tid":388956,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【「堅拒中大政治審查 捍衛學子言論自由」論壇】","createTime":"2017-09-05T23:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T12:08:00.000Z","uid":28366,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b68e11ba6b83c8e01034ca75795af47e2736713f","tid":388956,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T23:05:54.000Z","msg":"【「堅拒中大政治審查 捍衛學子言論自由」論壇】<br />\n<br />\n近日中大校園出現有關「香港獨立」宣傳品，中大校方粗暴干預學生會管理場地，打壓學生言論自由，本會幹事正在留守於文化廣場，阻止校方拆去相關橫額。<br />\n<br />\n本會希望藉著今次論壇引起中大同學以至公眾的討論，討論內容會圍繞言論自由、員生共治以及校園應否談「港獨」。<br />\n<br />\n日期：九月六日<br />\n時間：下午十二時半至二時<br />\n地點：香港中文大學文化廣場<br />\n<br />\n論壇嘉賓：<br />\n香港民族黨發言人 周浩輝<br />\n前中大學生會會長 周竪峰<br />\n本土民主前線召集人 黃台仰<br />\n前中大學生會會長 張秀賢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21317751_1579986365397100_5309319838833118056_n.jpg?oh=4b33cf4924ea3a19b4562d2bf7e39da0&amp;oe=5A5CE996\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21317751_1579986365397100_5309319838833118056_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4b33cf4924ea3a19b4562d2bf7e39da0%26oe%3D5A5CE996&h=83e059f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CUHK.SU/photos/a.416078851787863.103438.416069858455429/1579986365397100/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCUHK.SU%2Fphotos%2Fa.416078851787863.103438.416069858455429%2F1579986365397100%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=KD%2FBXRQF1n%2F%2FQhBJth2bkWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=155fcf3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CUHK.SU/photos/a.416078851787863.103438.416069858455429/1579986365397100/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"4d09edfd658d5a1708c7a9a0da0935fa9fc74848","tid":388956,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T23:08:52.000Z","msg":"都冇主張永續基本法=港獨既香港總統陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cceea29539ff57c3e2efe12a5286dfc25ce8116f","tid":388956,"uid":72681,"like